commitResults.messageTitle: Extract the concept of an IngredientReference
commitResults.messageBody:
this is separate from the concept of an Ingredient. It makes no
sense for a Recipe to hold references to Ingredients, especially
given that an Ingredient also holds an expiry date.

commitResults.messageBody:
Currently there is:
- Mass (eg. 250g of butter)
- Volume (eg. 300ml of milk, 3 tsp of cinnamon)
- Count (eg. 7 eggs)
